jobSpec.command: #!/bin/bash;#CSUB -J cubevnc;vncpath=$HOME/.vnc;if [ ! -d $vncpath ];then mkdir $vncpath;fi;export XDG_RUNTIME_DIR=$vncpath;vncwdfile=$vncpath/pw`echo $CB_HOSTS | cut -f1 -d ' '`.$CB_JOBID;sessionfile=$vncpath/session.$CB_JOBID;xstart=$vncpath/xstartup.$CB_JOBID;vnctop=$CB_ENVDIR/skyformvnc;vncbin=${vnctop}/bin;printf 'ysFrjJdi;ysFrjJdj;' | $vncbin/vncpasswd -f > $vncwdfile;chmod 600 $vncwdfile;head -2 $vnctop/openbox/xstartup > $xstart;echo paraview_job >> $xstart;echo exitcode=\$? >> $xstart;echo kill \$PID >> $xstart;echo exit \$exitcode >> $xstart;chmod +x $xstart;sid=`$vncbin/vncserver -geometry 1900x1060 -rfbauth $vncwdfile -autokill -name Desktop$CB_JOBID -xstartup $xstart 2>&1 | grep display | cut -d':' -f2 | cut -d' ' -f1`;process=`$vncbin/vncserver -list | grep -P ":$sid\t" | awk '{print $2}'`;if [ _$process == '_' ]; then;  echo Cannot start VNC session;  rm -f $vncwdfile $xstart;  exit 1;fi;echo $HOSTNAME $sid > $sessionfile;function sighd(){;  $vncbin/vncserver -kill :$sid;rm -f $vncwdfile $xstart $sessionfile; cat $vncpath/$HOSTNAME\:$sid.log;  exit 1;};trap sighd SIGINT SIGTERM;while true; do;  sleep 2;process=`$vncbin/vncserver -list | grep -P ":$sid\t" | awk '{print $2}'`;  if [ _$process == '_' ]; then;    rm -f $vncwdfile $xstart $sessionfile;    break;   fi;done; cat $vncpath/$HOSTNAME\:$sid.log
